elements.name: Book the hotel and cancel the booked hotel in booked itinerary page

steps.name: User should be successfully logged in, verify the text message  "Hello Shanmathi22!"
User search for a hotel by filling the search conditions
User verify the select hotel page after search the hotel "Select Hotel"
User select the hotel, click the continue button
User enter the booking details, click the BookNow button
User verfiy the booking confirmation page "Booking Confirmation" and order Id is generated
User click the My Itinerary button, search the booked hotel order id
User click the cancel button to cancel the booked hotel
user verify the cancel message "The booking has been cancelled."

name: Book and Cancel the Hotel in Adactin Hotel
